description: Say Conch is making its way through Mount Juliet and bringing a mouthwatering selection of Caribbean cuisine to the hungry crowds of this lucky Tennessee town.This veteran owned & operated trailer is where you’ll find delicious conch dishes like fritters and salads, as well as curried chicken & lamb, blackened grouper burgers, BBQ or Jerk wings, and all sorts of savory sides like mac & cheese, peas & rice, or delightfully tasty fried plantains. If you're craving a meat-free meal, a couple of exciting new additions to the menu include the Vegan Burger and Vegan Buffalo Cauliflower "Wings". For all this and much more, come on out to Say Conch (or invite them to cater your next big event) so that you and your guests can order up a refreshing virgin colada or daiquiri, and savor the vibes & flavors of Caribbean bliss.
name: Say Conch
